Subject: [PATCH 0550/1187] staging:iio:accel:adis16201 unwind use of IIO_CHAN
 macro.

commit e81dafe94228799fa33dd98e602f269d234cbac2	upstream

This macro is being removed to simplify ongoing maintenance
so we need to unwind and remaining users.

